企業經營專討                            


  	Though the course title is seminar, this course is about research methodologies. Our effort in achieving each of the objectives will assume an uneven weight distribution, which is reflective of the current and future trends in the field of social science. This course does not cover statistics. However, a solid understanding of statistics helps a lot in learning this course. We emphasize more on the conceptual reasoning. Therefore the ability to link your own domain knowledge/theories and appropriate research methods is essential in this course. Any forms of empirical supports beyond the conceptual building will be highly appreciated but not mandatory. Class participation is highly appreciated, too. Good class interactions benefit students and the instructor because it impresses the students and the instructor has a clearer idea to preside over the class during the semester. 

課程教育目標 

A. 溝通技巧B. 創新與解決問題能力D. 全球化視野E. 道德、技術及專業度 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

[基本素養]國際視野
訓練學生以全球性視野思考[核心能力]寫作能力
培養良好寫作能力創新能力
具備創新能力創意解決問題能力
利用創意方式及思考解決策略性問題分析能力
具備良好分析能力專業技能
具備專業技能 
